        "notes": {
            "4127d540-c757-4fe3-8921-e1da8429fdd5": {
                "content": "This version currently gets temperation in Farenheit for list of dates and hours for USA zip codes. \nNeed to enhance this pipeline  to add paramter to either call USA or CAN http client to get temperatures for dates and times.\n",
